{"tid":719564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登班道德塔利班先係真正最仆街既人","createTime":"2018-06-27T13:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T15:06:54.000Z","uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb2054910371993be1262c5813c1dc536010021","tid":719564,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"成日話道德淪喪點點點 見人講兩句風涼話又幫班廢老悲天憫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解呢度咁多人見到廢老比人殺好撚心涼?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為呢班仆街日日都欺壓年輕人 想佢地死 想佢地做一世奴隸 對想反抗既人冷嘲熱諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最無同情心 最道德淪喪既根本係你班出黎指指點點既仆街 同心愛白人既黑奴無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb669a856cb5bc883ee92af94c6d19e5d5f8942","tid":719564,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"神經病"},{"pid":"b91e02fc20b81bdee526793872afc2891037fc60","tid":719564,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb669a856cb5bc883ee92af94c6d19e5d5f8942","tid":719564,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"神經病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"死番去飲食台追個臭豆腐絲打啦incel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc537c67bbc7247ef718b78961a8baa6bac6c44b","tid":719564,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a603e57832e9cd6c903a34fda35d3856d713248c","tid":719564,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"Email 出黎講兩句"}]}